descr: "The Care Team includes all the people and organizations who plan to participate in the coordination and delivery of care for a patient."

fields.name: role
fields.descr: "Indicates specific responsibility of an individual within the care team, such as \"Primary care physician\", \"Trained social worker counselor\", \"Caregiver\", etc."

fields.name: member
fields.descr: "The specific person or organization who is participating/expected to participate in the care team."

fields.name: period
fields.descr: "Indicates when the specific member or organization did (or is intended to) come into effect and end."
